    {
        "content": "<p>What do y'all think of renaming this WG as the rustc-guide WG</p>",
        "id": 183948635,
        "sender_full_name": "nikomatsakis",
        "timestamp": 1576857993
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I've heard some people get confused that the role of the learning WG is to help people <em>learn rust</em></p>",
        "id": 183948649,
        "sender_full_name": "nikomatsakis",
        "timestamp": 1576858007
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>as opposed to learning about <em>rustc</em></p>",
        "id": 183948658,
        "sender_full_name": "nikomatsakis",
        "timestamp": 1576858014
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and it seems like rustc-guide is the current focus anyhow</p>",
        "id": 183948667,
        "sender_full_name": "nikomatsakis",
        "timestamp": 1576858022
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I definitely agree with the idea</p>",
        "id": 183949182,
        "sender_full_name": "Santiago Pastorino",
        "timestamp": 1576858355
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>the goals of the wg are also about rustc-guide and API docs which we are not really doing, so I prefer to have something that shows a bit more the focus of the group</p>",
        "id": 183949230,
        "sender_full_name": "Santiago Pastorino",
        "timestamp": 1576858396
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yep, that also makes sense to me</p>",
