        "sender_full_name": "mark-i-m",
        "timestamp": 1576864039
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I agree with that, but we won't rename the rustc-guide to rustc-dev-guide or something for now? I remember this issue: <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc-guide/issues/470\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc-guide/issues/470\">https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc-guide/issues/470</a></p>",
